INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================


Dependencies
~~~~~~~~~~~~

 * Python 2.4

 * antlr <http://www.antlr.org>

 * GNU make
 
 * pygtk for gui
 
 * graphviz


Building 
~~~~~~~~

1. Make the necessary modifications to the configuration variables on the top
   of the Makefile.

2. To build all the generated python code, do:

     make all

3. To run all the tests, do:

     make tests


Running
~~~~~~~

 * To see the assembly translation do:

     python util/translate.py examples/ex*.s

 * To play around with the GUI do:

     python idc.py

   You will need pygtk for that.
